Methodist</link></causal_agent>
</physical_entity>
.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref> She is a 2000 graduate of <education wordnetid="100883297" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../081/4606081.xml">
Park View High School (Loudoun County, Virginia)</link></education>
