<p>

In 2007, Burton started a production company called Southern Gothic Productions.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref> She appeared in <group wordnetid="100031264" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../873/2004873.xml">
Jack's Mannequin</link></group>
 video, "The Mixed Tape" as [Peyton Sawyer].<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref> Later, Burton recorded a song for the  called <it>Peyton's Podcast Mix</it>.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%228%22])">8</ref> </p>
<p>

In 2008, Burton starred in the independent movie <it><movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../467/11395467.xml">
The List</link></movie>
</it> as Jo Johnston. The film will be released on <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../733/2733.xml">
April 25</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../825/35825.xml">
2008</link>. Burton is currently filming a major motion picture called <it><literary_composition wordnetid="106364329" confidence="0.8">
<written_communication wordnetid="106349220" confidence="0.8">
<writing wordnetid="106362953" confidence="0.8">
