</fiction>
</writing>
</written_communication>
</literary_composition>
</it> based on the 2002 novel, Burton will play  Deborah Owens.  Production began on <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../987/15987.xml">
January 7</link> <fundamental_quantity wordnetid="113575869" confidence="0.8">
