<p>

Burton's newest project is titled <it>The Sacrifice</it>, and it is based on another book by Robert Whitlow (<it>The List</it>). She will be reunited with Malcolm McDowell and Gary Wheeler (director), who are also signed on for the project, which starts filming early next year.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref> </p>
<p>

Burton was nominated for a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../928/1506928.xml">
Teen Choice Award</link> for "Choice TV Actress in a Drama/Action Adventure" for <it>One Tree Hill</it> in 2004. Burton was also  nominated for the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../928/1506928.xml">
Teen Choice Award</link> "Choice Breakout TV Star - Female" for <it>One Tree Hill</it>, in 2004.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref></p>
<p>

In 2005, Burton was nominated for a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../928/1506928.xml">
Teen Choice Award</link> for "Choice TV Actress: Drama"
for <it>One Tree Hill</it>.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%2210%22])">10</ref></p>

