<sec>
<st>
Personal life</st>
<p>

Burton has three younger brothers.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref></p>
<p>

She and husband Ian Prange, an assistant-director for <it>One Tree Hill</it>, reside together in Wilmington, North Carolina, where the show is filmed. She has a cat named after writer <person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<writer wordnetid="110794014" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<critic wordnetid="109979321" confidence="0.9173553029164789">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../549/9549.xml">
Edgar Allan Poe</link></critic>
</writer>
</person>
,<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref> and is close friends with fellow <it>One Tree Hill</it> stars <actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../733/4019733.xml">
Bethany Joy Galeotti</link></actor>
 and <actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../050/1640050.xml">
Sophia Bush</link></actor>
.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref> Burton's hobbies include collecting antiques, knitting and crocheting.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref></p>
<p>

In May 2007, Burton ranked #77 in the <it><magazine wordnetid="106595351" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../988/241988.xml">
Maxim</link></magazine>
</it> Hot 100 List of 2007.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%2211%22])">11</ref> She has also appeared on the cover of the November 2006 edition of Maxim with <it><series wordnetid="108457976" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../957/999957.xml">
One Tree Hill</link></series>
</it> co-stars, Sophia Bush and <actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../819/5497819.xml">
Danneel Harris</link></actor>
. In previous years, Burton has ranked #2 on Femme Fatales: The 50 Sexiest Women of 2005 and named #12 on <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../909/365909.xml">
Much Music</link>'s 20 Hottest Women of 2003.</p>

